caption.center: Metcalf, Darcy Ray v. Board of Parole and Post-Prison Supervision.

opinion.opinion_text: Petitions For Review Dismissed. Petitioner on review field a motion to dismiss the Petition for review and the petition for parole review. The motion is granted. The petition for review and the petition for judicial review are dismissed.Page 475
